1. base premium for policy = sum of item bases  
2. item-specific modifiers (cursed, high enchantment) ‚Üí applied to affected item's base
3. policy-wide modifiers (loyalty, first-insurance, follow-up) ‚Üí applied to policy base (not the modified total)
4. processing fee

